query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b1) */ select b1.name,
count(*)
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('boot',
'hard-drive',
'memory',
'microsoft-excel',
'security',
'shell',
'terminal',
'unix',
'usb',
'windows-xp',
'wireless-networking') AND s.site_name IN ('superuser')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 5 AND q1.favorite_count <= 5000
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND acc.website_url ilike '%code%'
inner join badge AS b1
on s.site_id = b1.site_id AND b1.user_id = u1.id group by b1.name order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
